                <div class="mb-3">
                    <h4 class="section-title">Key Highlights</h4>
                    <ul class="list-group">
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>User Interface:</strong> Designed a responsive and intuitive front-end using HTML, CSS, and Bootstrap.
                            The interface ensures easy navigation for users, providing a seamless experience across devices such as desktops, tablets, and smartphones.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Backend Development:</strong> Built with ASP.NET and C#, the system ensures modular and maintainable code for handling user interactions and backend processes efficiently.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Database:</strong> SQL Server was used to securely store and manage user data, consumption details, billing records, and usage history.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <h4 class="section-title">Core Features</h4>
                    <ul class="list-group">
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Real-Time Consumption Tracking:</strong> Allows users to monitor their electricity usage in real-time, providing detailed insights into daily, weekly, and monthly consumption patterns.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Bill Generation:</strong> Automatically calculates and generates electricity bills based on usage and applicable tariffs.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Payment Integration:</strong> Supports seamless online payment options for bill settlement, enhancing user convenience.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Usage Analytics:</strong> Provides detailed analytics and visualizations to help users understand and optimize their energy consumption.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Monthly Reports:</strong> Generates comprehensive monthly reports summarizing electricity usage, billing details, and cost breakdowns.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <h4 class="section-title">Security Measures</h4>
                    <ul class="list-group">
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Role-Based Access:</strong> Implements role-based access control to differentiate functionalities for administrators and consumers.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Data Encryption:</strong> Ensures all sensitive user data, including personal details and payment information, is encrypted for maximum security.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Activity Monitoring:</strong> Logs all system activities, ensuring transparency and providing audit trails for security purposes.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
